# Logo Assets

Place your logo files here:

- stars-white.png - White stars logo for dark backgrounds (navbar in dark mode)
- stars-black.png - Black stars logo for light backgrounds (navbar in light mode)
- full-white.png - Full logo with text for dark backgrounds (hero, footer in dark mode)
- full-black.png - Full logo with text for light backgrounds (hero, footer in light mode)

Recommended dimensions:
- Stars logos: 200x64px (will be displayed at ~100x32px)
- Full logos: 400x160px (will be displayed at various sizes)
